Why does everyone want to perform the mystical actions of fools.  I do
not understand this attitude.  Magic is so easy, it is as easy as
transmuting water, grain and maybe some salt into bread, using simple
tools, and simple energies readily available, and then consuming it,
or better still spreading the magic and sharing it with some one.  Why
is this so difficult.  The truth is the big magic is diluted, it is
long past the time when such is necessary.  We do not need astral
projection to see across the world, it is simpler to use the services
that are available.  We do not need all those fancy parlor tricks,
true magicians do not waste their time with such ridiculousness.  I
read here all about how to do this, and how to cast that.  The truth
is there is no difference between wishes and prayers, there is no
difference between casting and caring.  Put your energy into
everything you do and your life will be magical.  Leave the parlor
tricks to the fools who would use them to influence monarchs and
ignorant peasants.

The next time you want an easy way to clean your room, there is one,
it is called physical labor.  What is most misunderstood about witches
and magicians of the old myths is that they only provided for their
communities that which was needed, medicinal concoctions imbued with
positive energies, healthy foods with the love of tireless hands.  Yes
they held knowledge that others did not, but they were not amazing
knowledge today, they were such things as the ability to read and
write, which I still think is a bit of a mystery to some people.
There were those that could reshape the world, but only because they
could reshape perceptions.  They could shift shapes, because the
people wanted to see that happen.  We are not threatened any more.
Please stop this crap about persecution, we don't even know what that
is.  Our lives are not in jeopardy, there are no witch hunts any
more.  There is only ridicule from those of the established religions,
but they won't come to your house and lynch you, or burn you, so stop
this I am being mistreated bullshit and start making real magical
wonders like nice warm rolls, and home cooked meals.

I have this really nice book of spells, if you would like a couple ask
and I might give you one or two, but I warn you, they are really
simple, but after all simple is beautiful.

Sleep well;
James
